# CW Node Helper — Hero demo
# Record: vhs assets/tapes/hero.tape
Output assets/hero.gif
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set FontSize 14
Set FontFamily "SF Mono"
Set Theme "Builtin Dark"
Set Padding 20

Type "cwhelper" Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "DO-12345" Enter
Sleep 3s
Type "b" Sleep 500ms
Sleep 2s
Type "q" Enter
Sleep 1s
